 round a orc and sing kumbaya. I am about to think that some high level <BR>
verant employee is playing a warrior online because of some recent changes<BR>
 involving looting. Since only warriors and the super strength characters need <BR>
armor and heavy items only they benefit from the no item loot policy. I also <BR>
think if you are going to restrict or modify a class to be unable to use one of its<BR>
 mainstay abilities you should compensate them in some other way. I as a<BR>
 enchanter will strive to make verant pay for this slight in any way possible.<BR>
 Death to all Lighties, Brakanur Enchanter
